						<div class="postbody">I don't know if the sprite DMA can affect the PPU address in any way, but maybe you should set $2000 and $2005 after the DMA. Realistically, this (setting the scroll) wouldn't be the first thing in your NMI. You should set the scroll after all other PPU operations are done, since they mess with the PPU address (wich means they mess with the scrolling).
<br />
<br />Maybe this changes something?
<br />
