						<div class="postbody">Sprite 0 should always be set at a fixed location in the non-transparent part of your status bar. For instance, sprite 0 in <em>Super Mario Bros.</em> is a sliver of the coin image. Use sprites 1-63 for game objects.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

